packager - Manages the installation / removal of packages

This command will maintain thirdparty packages.
You may install applications or drivers with this command.

Action Parameter:
-i or --install        Install an application package
-r or --remove         Removes installed application
--install-driver       Install a driver
--remove-driver        Remove a driver

Usage: packager [action parameter] [specification]

Example:
packager -i myapplication.hxa
packager -r myapplication
